          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In some applications it may be preferable to wait for screen-refresh data synchronously, using this function. You should call this function in a thread other than the main event-processing thread. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As an alternative, Quartz also supports asynchronous notification—see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/1541774-cgregisterscreenrefreshcallback"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". If refresh callback functions are registered, this function should not be used."
            }
          ]
